Package: ggordiplots
Type: Package
Title: Make 'ggplot2' Versions of Vegan's Ordiplots
Version: 0.4.1
Authors@R: c(person("John", "Quensen", email = "quensenj@msu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7669-1595"),
           person("Gavin L.", "Simpson", role = "aut"),
           person("Jari", "Oksanen", role = "aut"))
Description: The 'vegan' package includes several functions for adding
    features to ordination plots: ordiarrows, ordibubbles, ordiellipse,
    ordihull, ordispider, ordisurf. This package adds these same
    features to ordination plots made with 'ggplot2'.
